seller.oneLinerTitle: With over 1,000 orders completed, I do what I do for the ONE
seller.description: I Like Words and I Love Serving People! I'm Zach Rippey and I went from slanging jokes on stage to writing top-notch speeches and scripts for clients all over the globe. When I'm not writing, I'm recording a weekly podcast called "I Like Birds." We have been on the air for 3 years, with 150 plus episodes, and are ranked in the Top 2% of all podcasts. I'm also an author who hit the number #1 new release on Amazon in my category for my book "21 Days in Africa." I'm a husband and father of 3 boys who provides for them by using the gifts God gave me to help others! I love what I do! Let's Work!
